!-   ===========  ALL OBJECTS IN CLASS: OUTPUT:METER ===========

  Output:Meter,Heating:EnergyTransfer,Hourly;

  Output:Meter,Cooling:EnergyTransfer,Hourly;

!-   ===========  ALL OBJECTS IN CLASS: OUTPUT:SQLITE ===========

  Output:SQLite,
    SimpleAndTabular,        !- Option Type
    UseOutputControlTableStyle;  !- Unit Conversion for Tabular Data

!-   ===========  ALL OBJECTS IN CLASS: OUTPUT:DIAGNOSTICS ===========

  Output:Diagnostics,
    DisplayAdvancedReportVariables,  !- Key 1
    DisplayExtraWarnings;    !- Key 2

